The '''[[AFC Youth Championship]] 1972''' was held in [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]].

==Teams==
The following teams entered the tournament:

* {{fbu|20|BRU}}
* {{fbu|20|Burma|1948}}
* {{fbu|20|HKG|1959}}
* {{fbu|20|IND}}
* {{fbu|20|IDN}}
* {{fbu|20|IRI|1964}}
* {{fbu|20|ISR}}
* {{fbu|20|JPN}}
* {{fbu|20|Khmer Republic}}
* {{fbu|20|LAO|1952}}
* {{fbu|20|MYS}}
* {{fbu|20|NEP}}
* {{fbu|20|PHL|1936}}
* {{fbu|20|SGP}}
* {{fbu|20|KOR}}
* {{fbu|20|TWN}}
* {{fbu|20|THA}} (host)

